;w=1200&amp;q=75 2x" src="/_next/image?url=%2Fvideo_consultations%2Fclinical-documentation-integration.jpg&amp;w=1200&amp;q=75"/></div></div><div class="lg:w-full space-y-8 lg:order-2"><div class="inline-block"><span class="bg-purple-light/20 text-purple-accent px-4 py-2 rounded-full text-sm font-medium border border-purple-accent/30">Flusso di Lavoro Clinico Integrato</span></div><div><h2 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl lg:text-6xl font-bold text-slate-dark mb-6 leading-tight">Flusso di Lavoro Clinico Integrato</h2><p class="text-xl text-slate-600 leading-relaxed max-w-xl">Documentazione clinica completa con appunti, prescrizioni e fatturazione perfettamente integrati nel tuo flusso di lavoro esistente.</p></div><div class="space-y-6"><div class="flex items-start gap-3"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-circle-check-big h-6 w-6 text-purple-accent flex-shrink-0 mt-1" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M21.801 10A10 10 0 1 1 17 3.335"></path><path d="m9 11 3 3L22 4"></path></svg><div><p class="text-lg text-slate-700">I medici possono visualizzare la cartella clinica del paziente durante la chiamata.</p></div></div><div class="flex items-start gap-3"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-circle-check-big h-6 w-6 text-purple-accent flex-shrink-0 mt-1" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M21.801 10A10 10 0 1 1 17 3.335"></path><path d="m9 11 3 3L22 4"></path></svg><div><p class="text-lg text-slate-700">Prendi appunti in tempo reale, che confluiscono nel registro degli incontri.</p></div></div><div class="flex items-start gap-3"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" str